    "f = 0.8·3.504 = 2.803 N; α = 3.504/0.15 = 23.36 rad/s²",
    "Verify with formula: a = g·sin30°/(1 + I/(mr²)) = 9.81·0.5/(1 + 2/5) = 4.905/1.4 = 3.504 ✓"
